00:21:04.425 --> 00:21:05.985
{\an8}FAMOUS INFLUENCER CLAIMS HE ADOPTED
A DOG BUT WAS SPOTTED AT A DOG FARM

00:21:06.065 --> 00:21:07.585
{\an8}AND THE DOG BEING SOLD THERE
HAS THE EXACT SAME MARKINGS

00:21:07.665 --> 00:21:09.305
HONESTLY, I'M DISAPPOINTED

00:21:09.385 --> 00:21:11.185
FAKE ADOPTION

00:21:38.625 --> 00:21:41.385
Guys, I checked.

00:21:41.905 --> 00:21:44.385
Jamie's absent today.
He said he's not feeling well.

00:21:44.465 --> 00:21:47.625
Ugh. It must be about
that latest dog-buying issue.

00:21:47.705 --> 00:21:49.065
Do you think it's true?

00:21:49.585 --> 00:21:51.385
It's obviously fake news.

00:21:51.465 --> 00:21:53.785
I agree.

00:21:53.865 --> 00:21:56.465
But I don't understand
why everyone believes it.

00:21:58.905 --> 00:22:01.225
Why is that?

00:22:01.745 --> 00:22:05.185
Honestly, is there anything else
we can do to help Jamie?

00:22:05.265 --> 00:22:07.105
Just to find the one who started it.

00:22:07.185 --> 00:22:09.225
Yeah, I'm actually curious now.

00:22:09.305 --> 00:22:11.705
Who is that jealous anti

00:22:11.785 --> 00:22:13.145
who stirred everything up?

00:22:14.785 --> 00:22:15.625
Oh.

00:22:16.545 --> 00:22:18.425
I remember

00:22:18.505 --> 00:22:21.185
that the account was named…

00:22:22.585 --> 00:22:23.985
"Pangstop."

00:22:26.065 --> 00:22:27.745
I wonder who that is too.

00:22:28.865 --> 00:22:33.265
Maybe it's someone closer than we think.

00:22:45.305 --> 00:22:47.825
PANGSTOP
#BANJAMIE

00:22:47.905 --> 00:22:50.945
WHAT? I RAISED MY HAND FIRST
WHY DIDN'T THEY CLAP FOR ME?

00:22:54.745 --> 00:22:56.545
DID HE REALLY ADOPT HER,
OR IS HE JUST LYING?

00:23:10.185 --> 00:23:12.665
PANGSTOP

00:23:12.745 --> 00:23:15.185
FAKE BACKSTORY

00:23:15.265 --> 00:23:16.225
DELETE ACCOUNT

00:23:29.465 --> 00:23:32.385
SO SURPRISED: HELLO, HONGTAE.
WHY DID YOU DELETE THAT POST?

00:23:40.985 --> 00:23:42.985
PANGSTOP

00:24:01.625 --> 00:24:03.385
Oh, Hongtae.

00:24:03.465 --> 00:24:05.305
Aren't you going to chemistry class?

00:24:05.385 --> 00:24:07.585
Everyone's already left.

00:24:10.385 --> 00:24:13.625
And what are you going to do
with that ruler?

00:24:13.705 --> 00:24:14.785
Nothing.

00:24:20.025 --> 00:24:21.265
By the way,

00:24:22.945 --> 00:24:24.825
what do you think about Jamie?

00:24:29.065 --> 00:24:30.265
Why do you ask?

00:24:30.785 --> 00:24:33.025
Jamie's been in the news lately.

00:24:33.105 --> 00:24:34.865
So I was just wondering,

00:24:34.945 --> 00:24:36.905
what do you think about Jamie?

00:24:43.545 --> 00:24:44.945
He's nice.

00:24:47.545 --> 00:24:49.465
Everyone likes him.

00:24:50.905 --> 00:24:53.025
So that means…

00:24:54.585 --> 00:24:57.305
you like Jamie too?

00:25:04.305 --> 00:25:05.185
Really?

00:25:08.585 --> 00:25:10.225
It's a shame.

00:25:19.425 --> 00:25:21.185
I might as well confess.

00:25:22.185 --> 00:25:25.905
I'm actually pretty indifferent
about Jamie.

00:25:28.425 --> 00:25:32.425
But I pretend to like him
because I'm afraid of having no friends.

00:25:33.825 --> 00:25:36.345
Jamie seems kind of fake.

00:25:37.585 --> 00:25:40.865
No wonder the ban movement keeps growing.

00:25:42.145 --> 00:25:43.705
I think…

00:25:44.225 --> 00:25:46.705
if they push it hard enough,

00:25:47.225 --> 00:25:51.265
#BanJamie could definitely trend
to number one.

00:25:53.425 --> 00:25:55.825
Jamie should suffer a real impact.

00:25:57.865 --> 00:25:59.025
Oops.

00:26:00.185 --> 00:26:01.585
What did I just say?

00:26:04.385 --> 00:26:07.465
But you wouldn't get involved
in something like that anyway, right?

00:26:12.265 --> 00:26:16.105
Let's just forget about it.

00:26:39.985 --> 00:26:42.665
Everyone, start the war.

00:26:42.745 --> 00:26:45.025
Push the hashtag to number one.

00:26:45.865 --> 00:26:47.825
Let the whole country know.

00:26:47.905 --> 00:26:50.105
Ban Jamie!

00:26:50.185 --> 00:26:51.905
HOPE YOUR MOM GETS GROPED LIKE THIS TOO

00:26:51.985 --> 00:26:53.705
GOOD-LOOKING BUT FILTHY

00:26:55.225 --> 00:26:57.985
Save Jamie! Go!

00:26:58.065 --> 00:26:59.505
IT'S HIS DOG. WHY DOES IT BOTHER YOU?

00:26:59.585 --> 00:27:01.065
NO ONE IS BETTER THAN YOUR MOM

00:27:10.145 --> 00:27:12.145
Don't be afraid of them, dear! Fight them!

00:27:14.185 --> 00:27:16.145
Fight them!

00:27:44.785 --> 00:27:46.505
You jealous pieces of shit.

00:27:46.585 --> 00:27:50.305
You've got issues? Broken family?
Do I need to spell it out?

00:27:51.665 --> 00:27:53.705
Don't even.
You're just pretending to be nice

00:27:53.785 --> 00:27:56.105
because you want Jamie
to be your boyfriend. It's obvious.

00:28:02.505 --> 00:28:05.625
Guys, the dog farm just posted something.

00:28:08.225 --> 00:28:09.505
WE'D LIKE TO CONFIRM THIS IS TRUE

00:28:09.585 --> 00:28:11.705
MR. JAMIE PURCHASED A DOG
FROM OUR FARM ON MAY 22, 2023

00:28:11.785 --> 00:28:14.185
PLOT TWIST #BANJAMIE

00:28:35.905 --> 00:28:38.665
I've known for a while
but didn't dare speak up.

00:28:38.745 --> 00:28:40.225
I'VE KNOWN FOR A WHILE
BUT DIDN'T DARE SPEAK UP

00:28:40.305 --> 00:28:42.025
I'M READY TO BEAT HIM UP

00:29:17.585 --> 00:29:21.385
Hey, everyone. I think

00:29:21.465 --> 00:29:23.705
I found something strange.

00:29:27.625 --> 00:29:29.945
It looks like the accounts named

00:29:30.585 --> 00:29:31.745
Rrdaji,

00:29:35.225 --> 00:29:36.585
Papa Meow,

00:29:38.065 --> 00:29:39.465
God of War,

00:29:40.385 --> 00:29:42.305
Let me educate you,

00:29:42.385 --> 00:29:44.945
and Pangstop…

00:29:46.705 --> 00:29:48.465
…might all belong to the same person.

00:29:50.265 --> 00:29:51.425
Impressive, right?

00:29:53.385 --> 00:29:55.705
I posted the original source in the group.

00:29:55.785 --> 00:29:57.185
You can go say hi.

00:30:11.785 --> 00:30:12.945
- Hey!
- Follow him!

00:30:13.025 --> 00:30:14.665
- Hey!
- Where are you going?

00:30:14.745 --> 00:30:16.105
Hey!

00:30:20.185 --> 00:30:21.265
IDIOT

00:30:25.465 --> 00:30:26.385
HELLO

00:30:31.665 --> 00:30:32.585
I found you.

00:30:32.665 --> 00:30:33.705
- Damn you.
- Come here!

00:30:33.785 --> 00:30:34.905
{\an8}What?!

00:30:36.785 --> 00:30:37.745
Let go!

00:30:37.825 --> 00:30:40.025
So here is where you are.
Reveal yourself.

00:30:40.105 --> 00:30:41.385
Popcorn's ready.

00:30:42.465 --> 00:30:44.105
- No!
- You're not getting away today.

00:30:56.865 --> 00:30:58.465
No!

00:30:59.065 --> 00:31:00.225
Don't!

00:31:01.745 --> 00:31:03.065
Shit!

00:31:03.145 --> 00:31:03.985
Let go!

00:31:07.785 --> 00:31:09.705
NANNO:
OOPS. A PHOTO JUST DROPPED

00:31:30.225 --> 00:31:31.345
Hey!

00:31:49.625 --> 00:31:51.945
I'LL GO TO KOSHIEN IN 5 YEARS

00:31:57.945 --> 00:31:59.185
Shit.

00:32:08.385 --> 00:32:10.105
GUYS

00:32:10.185 --> 00:32:11.905
I NEED TO SHARE THIS

00:32:11.985 --> 00:32:13.265
LET ME GET ON MY X

00:32:16.065 --> 00:32:18.545
OH, TURNS OUT IT WAS SOMEONE CLOSE

00:32:20.905 --> 00:32:22.705
THE ONE NOBODY WANTS TO BE FRIENDS WITH

00:32:31.345 --> 00:32:32.545
THE ONE WHO MAKES TRASH CONTENT

00:32:34.105 --> 00:32:34.985
ATTENTION SEEKER

00:32:39.345 --> 00:32:40.705
Damn it.

00:32:43.425 --> 00:32:44.945
YOU WANNA BE FAMOUS?

00:32:45.025 --> 00:32:47.145
I'LL HELP

00:32:47.225 --> 00:32:48.505
JAKRAPAT HONGTRAKUL
CLASS 6/4, BOWORN SCHOOL

00:32:51.385 --> 00:32:52.345
HE'S SO CRINGE

00:32:59.785 --> 00:33:01.145
Leave me alone!

00:33:01.225 --> 00:33:02.345
WHAT KIND OF FAMILY DID YOU GROW UP IN?

00:33:06.665 --> 00:33:08.705
YOU'RE A TERRIBLE PARENT

00:33:17.225 --> 00:33:18.105
PATHETIC

00:33:18.185 --> 00:33:19.225
CAN IT GET ANY WORSE THAN THIS?

00:33:19.305 --> 00:33:20.185
EXPOSE HIM

00:33:27.265 --> 00:33:28.625
Stop!

00:33:46.745 --> 00:33:48.625
Leave me alone!

00:33:48.705 --> 00:33:52.625
IT'S GOING VIRAL

00:33:52.705 --> 00:33:53.705
Damn you!

00:33:54.465 --> 00:33:56.105
Stop!

00:34:48.665 --> 00:34:49.865
Why?

00:34:53.545 --> 00:34:55.345
Even though

00:34:56.905 --> 00:34:58.265
Jamie

00:34:59.065 --> 00:35:01.065
lied to everyone

00:35:03.025 --> 00:35:05.585
and didn't even adopt that dog,

00:35:07.985 --> 00:35:10.705
why are you still helping him?

00:35:11.385 --> 00:35:12.785
Helping?

00:35:14.705 --> 00:35:16.225
Helping Jamie?

00:35:17.505 --> 00:35:21.025
No. I wasn't helping Jamie.

00:35:23.265 --> 00:35:25.705
I've been helping you all along.

00:35:29.265 --> 00:35:30.505
Helping me?

00:35:32.385 --> 00:35:33.425
Yes.

00:35:41.385 --> 00:35:44.545
{\an8}IS IT HARD TO TAKE CARE OF A FEMALE DOG?
YOU HAVE TO BE CAREFUL, RIGHT?

00:35:50.385 --> 00:35:51.985
You're trying to cover it up

00:35:52.065 --> 00:35:54.625
because you really did
sexually harass your dog, right?

00:35:54.705 --> 00:35:56.185
Yeah. He should be banned.

00:36:00.225 --> 00:36:02.145
But what a surprise.

00:36:03.345 --> 00:36:05.985
You went this far.

00:36:08.345 --> 00:36:09.905
No one in class

00:36:10.505 --> 00:36:13.385
can compete with you.

00:36:14.905 --> 00:36:16.305
Hongtae,

00:36:16.825 --> 00:36:19.265
you must really love Jamie.

00:36:26.105 --> 00:36:27.185
What are you talking about?

00:36:27.825 --> 00:36:28.665
Oh?

00:36:29.985 --> 00:36:32.265
You still don't realize

00:36:32.345 --> 00:36:34.945
what the outcome of this war is?

00:36:55.825 --> 00:36:57.465
Did you really think

00:36:57.545 --> 00:36:59.945
the account of a random boy

00:37:00.465 --> 00:37:02.105
playing with a dog every day

00:37:02.945 --> 00:37:04.585
with nothing new or interesting

00:37:05.105 --> 00:37:07.505
could reach 500,000 followers on its own?

00:37:11.265 --> 00:37:13.025
What you did

00:37:13.105 --> 00:37:15.945
made everyone focus on Jamie

00:37:17.745 --> 00:37:21.065
because humans love conflict.

00:37:21.705 --> 00:37:23.505
They love violence.

00:37:23.585 --> 00:37:25.185
Right?

00:37:25.705 --> 00:37:27.265
I won't accept that!

00:37:27.345 --> 00:37:29.905
Without your hatred,

00:37:29.985 --> 00:37:32.665
Jamie wouldn't have gotten
this much attention.

00:37:36.945 --> 00:37:39.025
It was fun.

00:37:44.265 --> 00:37:45.665
Very fun.

00:37:48.745 --> 00:37:50.025
Fight them!

00:37:57.705 --> 00:37:58.945
Fight them!

00:38:23.665 --> 00:38:25.545
I finally found you.

00:38:28.145 --> 00:38:29.345
A stalker?

00:38:30.785 --> 00:38:34.825
But you could only find me online, Sky.

00:38:36.505 --> 00:38:37.665
Maybe not.

00:38:51.505 --> 00:38:52.745
Go!

00:39:03.865 --> 00:39:05.185
Anyway,

00:39:06.465 --> 00:39:07.745
in the end,

00:39:07.825 --> 00:39:12.065
this war ends with you being sacrificed.

00:39:14.025 --> 00:39:15.105
But…

00:39:15.625 --> 00:39:17.225
don't worry.

00:39:18.505 --> 00:39:20.865
You've got plenty of fellow martyrs.

00:39:31.905 --> 00:39:33.345
Everyone,

00:39:33.425 --> 00:39:36.145
I'm sorry for disappearing recently.

00:39:37.105 --> 00:39:38.865
I was seriously sick.

00:39:40.545 --> 00:39:42.265
But I'm getting better now,

00:39:42.785 --> 00:39:44.585
thanks to all of your support.

00:39:47.985 --> 00:39:49.705
There's another thing

00:39:49.785 --> 00:39:51.825
I want to tell everyone.

00:39:51.905 --> 00:39:53.505
Lately,

00:39:53.585 --> 00:39:56.825
a group of people
has been trying to defame me.

00:39:57.985 --> 00:39:59.825
So I've decided

00:40:00.785 --> 00:40:02.585
to sue both the ringleader,

00:40:03.105 --> 00:40:04.825
whom I now know the identity of,

00:40:05.425 --> 00:40:06.985
and all the followers involved.

00:40:08.505 --> 00:40:11.505
At first, I hesitated,
not sure if I should sue.

00:40:11.585 --> 00:40:14.345
But everyone told me

00:40:14.425 --> 00:40:16.185
I should set an example,

00:40:17.305 --> 00:40:18.785
so I have to do this.

00:40:20.585 --> 00:40:23.185
Thank you all so much,

00:40:23.265 --> 00:40:26.665
including the people
who sent me information.

00:40:26.745 --> 00:40:28.785
Hong says thank you too, right?

00:40:28.865 --> 00:40:30.265
Thank the fans.

00:40:30.345 --> 00:40:32.665
PANGSTOP

00:40:36.985 --> 00:40:39.305
{\an8}You know that your support

00:40:39.385 --> 00:40:44.145
is the best energy for me and Hong, right?

00:41:21.305 --> 00:41:22.545
Five,

00:41:23.185 --> 00:41:24.385
four,

00:41:24.945 --> 00:41:26.585
three,

00:41:27.265 --> 00:41:28.505
two,

00:41:29.585 --> 00:41:30.985
one.

00:41:37.985 --> 00:41:39.185
Zero.

00:41:52.745 --> 00:41:54.385
Hongtae.

00:41:55.225 --> 00:41:59.185
You're the cutest anti-fan ever.

00:41:59.865 --> 00:42:01.105
Did you know that?

00:42:40.305 --> 00:42:46.585
Jamie! Jamie!

00:43:40.705 --> 00:43:42.145
It's my body.

00:43:42.225 --> 00:43:44.625
I can do whatever I want with it.
I can show whatever I want.

00:43:45.985 --> 00:43:47.345
It's my business.

00:43:47.425 --> 00:43:49.745
My body, my choice.

00:43:52.345 --> 00:43:54.105
The whole idea

00:43:54.185 --> 00:43:57.225
that our bodies belong to us

00:43:58.225 --> 00:43:59.785
is amazing.

00:44:02.625 --> 00:44:05.465
{\an8}If you hadn't inspired me,

00:44:06.025 --> 00:44:08.945
we probably wouldn't be having
this much fun right now.

00:46:05.745 --> 00:46:09.745
